Services are provided “AS IS.” We work hard to offer great services, but we can’t guarantee any minimum level of quality services (which may depend on factors beyond our control, such as the quality of internet access and equipment).  To the fullest extent permitted by law, we make no warranties, either express or implied, about the services. The services are provided “AS IS.” We also disclaim any implied warranties and merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, client enjoyment, and non-infringement, and any warranties arising out of course of dealing or usage of trade. The laws of certain jurisdictions or states do not allow limitations on implied warranties. To the extent such warranties cannot be disclaimed under the laws of your jurisdiction, we limit the duration and remedies of such warranties to the fullest extent permissible under those laws.2:[["$","nav",null,{"className":"nav","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/","className":"nav-logo","children":[["$","img",null,{"className":"nav-logo-mark","src":"/playplace-app-icon.png","alt":"Play Spotter","width":192,"height":192,"decoding":"async"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"nav-logo-text","children":"Play Spotter"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"nav-links","children":[["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/discover","children":"Discover"}],["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/map","children":"Map"}],["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/events","children":"Events"}],["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/lists","children":"Saved"}],["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/advertise","children":"Advertise"}],["$","$L6",null,{"href":"/support","children":"Support"}],["$","$L7",null,{}]]}]]}]}],["$","main",null,{"className":"legal-page","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container legal","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"$undefined"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"updated","children":["Last Updated: ","$undefined",""]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"legal-markdown","children":[["$","hr","hr-0",{}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-0",{"children":"title: Advertiser Agreement\ndescription: Play Spotter advertiser agreement governing ad submissions, approval, and display.\nversion: \"1.1\"\nlastUpdated: \"April 15, 2026\""}],"\n",["$","p","p-0",{"children":"This Advertiser Agreement governs the submission, approval, and display of advertising content within Play Spotter. By submitting an advertisement and completing payment, you agree to the following terms."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-1",{"children":"1. Authorization"}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"children":"You represent and warrant that you are authorized to act on behalf of the business, all submitted information is accurate and truthful, and you have legal rights to use all submitted images, logos, and content."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-2",{"children":"2. Content Requirements"}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"children":"All advertising content must be family-friendly and appropriate for parents and caregivers using the service, comply with all applicable laws, not be false, harmful, obscene, fraudulent, defamatory, misleading, or deceptive, and not promote unsafe, illegal, obscene or harmful activities. We reserve the right to reject or remove any content at our discretion. The app is not directed at children, and advertising is not delivered to child accounts. Content shall not be designed and/or marketed toward those aged thirteen (13) years of age or below."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-3",{"children":"3. Approval & Publication"}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":"All advertisements are subject to review and approval. Payment does not guarantee approval or placement. We may request modifications prior to approval and may remove or pause ads at any time if they violate policies."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-4",{"children":"4. Campaign Terms"}],"\n",["$","p","p-4",{"children":"Ads will run for the selected duration and placement. Start dates may be adjusted based on approval timing. Placement is subject to availability and platform rules."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-5",{"children":"5. Payments & Refunds"}],"\n",["$","ul","ul-0",{"children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"children":"Payment is required prior to review or activation"}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"children":"If an ad is rejected before going live, we may issue a refund in line with this Agreement"}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"children":"You may cancel a campaign at any time; once an advertisement has gone live, cancellation does not entitle you to a refund for time already paid for"}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"children":"Chargebacks or fraudulent disputes may result in account suspension"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-6",{"children":"6. No Performance Guarantee"}],"\n",["$","p","p-5",{"children":"$8"}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-7",{"children":"7. Advertiser Responsibility"}],"\n",["$","p","p-6",{"children":"Advertisers are solely responsible for the accuracy of business information, customer interactions, fulfillment of services, and compliance with laws. We are not responsible for disputes between users and advertisers."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-8",{"children":"8. Limitation of Liability & Indemnification"}],"\n",["$","p","p-7",{"children":"To the fullest extent permitted by law, Play Spotter shall not be liable for indirect or consequential damages, loss of revenue or business opportunities, or issues arising from ad performance."}],"\n",["$","p","p-8",{"children":"Further, the Advertiser agrees to indemnify and hold Play Spotter and its officers, directors, employees and agents harmless from any and all claims, damages, liabilities, and costs (including reasonable legal and accounting fees) related to (a) your access or use of our services or third-party services, (b) your violation of these terms, or (c) your negligence or willful misconduct. OUR TOTAL LIABILITY TO YOU FOR ANY CLAIM ARISING FROM YOUR USE OF OUR ADVERTISING SERVICES SHALL NOT EXCEED THE AMOUNT YOU PAID TO US FOR THE ADVERTISING CAMPAIGN AT ISSUE."}],"\n",["$","p","p-9",{"children":"Any action, regardless of form, arising out of or relating to a dispute may be brought by either party not more than one (1) year after the cause of action has accrued."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-9",{"children":"9. License to Use Content/Intellectual Property"}],"\n",["$","p","p-10",{"children":"You grant us a limited, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to display your submitted content within the app, modify formatting to fit app layouts, and use content for review and moderation."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-10",{"children":"10. Termination"}],"\n",["$","p","p-11",{"children":"We may suspend or terminate campaigns if terms are violated, payment issues occur, or fraudulent activity is detected."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-11",{"children":"11. Modifications"}],"\n",["$","p","p-12",{"children":"We may update this Agreement at any time. Continued use of the advertising platform constitutes acceptance of updates."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-12",{"children":"12. Acceptance"}],"\n",["$","p","p-13",{"children":"By submitting your advertisement, you confirm that you have read and agree to this Agreement, you understand payment does not guarantee results, and you accept all terms outlined above."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-13",{"children":"13. Governing Law"}],"\n",["$","p","p-14",{"children":"This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Nebraska, USA. Any legal proceedings shall be filed in Douglas County, Nebraska."}],"\n",["$","h2","h2-14",{"children":"14. Contact"}],"\n",["$","p","p-15",{"children":["$","a","a-0",{"href":"mailto:playplacefinder@gmail.com","children":"playplacefinder@gmail.com"}]}]]}]]}]}],["$","footer",null,{"className":"footer","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","a",null,{"className":"footer-credit-banner","href":"https://www.luchtapplications.com/","target":"_blank","rel":"noreferrer","aria-label":"Built by Lucht Applications","children":["$","img",null,{"src":"/built-by-lucht-applications.svg","alt":"Built by Lucht Applications","width":"1774","height":"887","loading":"lazy","decoding":"async"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"footer-links","children":[["$","$L6","/privacy",{"href":"/privacy","children":"Privacy Policy"}],["$","$L6","/terms",{"href":"/terms","children":"Terms of Service"}],["$","$L6","/delete-account",{"href":"/delete-account","children":"Delete account"}],["$","$L6","/advertise",{"href":"/advertise","children":"Advertise"}],["$","$L6","/",{"href":"/","children":"Home"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["© ",2026," Lucht Applications LLC — Play Spotter"]}]]}]}]]
